      <highlights>Low avalanche danger will prevail.</highlights>
      <comment>Only isolated dry avalanches are possible. They can be released, in particular by large loads, but they will be small in most cases. Individual avalanche prone locations are to be found on steep shady slopes at high altitude. &lt;br/> &lt;br/> As a consequence of warming during the day only isolated wet avalanches are possible.</comment>
